{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-working-with-text/working-with-text-lesson-j","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"top-working-with-text","challengeType":15,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Ako želite da imate listu stavki čiji red nije važan, kao što je lista za kupovinu stvari koje se mogu nabaviti u bilo kom redosledu, onda možete koristiti neuređenu listu.</p>\n<p>Neuređene liste se kreiraju korišćenjem elemenata <code>&#x3C;ul></code>, a svaki element unutar liste kreira se korišćenjem elemenata lista <code>&#x3C;li></code>.</p>\n<p>Svaki stavka u neuređenu listu počinje tačkom pred navodima:</p>\n<iframe allowfullscreen=\"true\" allowpaymentrequest=\"true\" allowtransparency=\"true\" class=\"cp_embed_iframe \" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"300\" width=\"100%\" name=\"cp_embed_1\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://codepen.io/TheOdinProjectExamples/embed/powjajd?height=300&amp;theme-id=dark&amp;default-tab=html%2Cresult&amp;slug-hash=powjajd&amp;user=TheOdinProjectExamples&amp;name=cp_embed_1\" style=\"width: 100%; overflow:hidden; display:block;\" title=\"CodePen Embed\" loading=\"lazy\" id=\"cp_embed_powjajd\"></iframe>\n<p>Ako umesto toga želite napraviti listu stavki čiji je redosled važan, kao što su uputstva korak po korak za recepte ili vaše 10 omiljenih televizijskih emisija, možete koristiti numerisanu listu.</p>\n<p>Strukturirane liste se kreiraju korišćenjem elementa <code>&#x3C;ol></code>. Svaki pojedinačni element unutar njega takođe se kreira korišćenjem elementa stavke liste <code>&#x3C;li></code>. Međutim, svaki element liste u strukturiranoj listi počinje brojem umesto toga:</p>\n<iframe allowfullscreen=\"true\" allowpaymentrequest=\"true\" allowtransparency=\"true\" class=\"cp_embed_iframe \" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"300\" width=\"100%\" name=\"cp_embed_2\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://codepen.io/TheOdinProjectExamples/embed/yLXYvYp?height=300&amp;theme-id=dark&amp;default-tab=html%2Cresult&amp;slug-hash=yLXYvYp&amp;user=TheOdinProjectExamples&amp;name=cp_embed_2\" style=\"width: 100%; overflow:hidden; display:block;\" title=\"CodePen Embed\" loading=\"lazy\" id=\"cp_embed_yLXYvYp\"></iframe>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Odin","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-working-with-text/working-with-text-lesson-j"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Koja vrsta etikete je HTML korišćena za kreiranje stavki liste unutar neuređenog i uređenog spiska?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><code>&#x3C;ol></code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>&#x3C;li></code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>&#x3C;ul></code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null}],"solution":2}],"scene":null,"superBlock":"the-odin-project","tests":[],"title":"Rad sa tekstualnim materijalom J","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/the-odin-project/#top-working-with-text","dashedName":"working-with-text-lesson-j","certification":"the-odin-project","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"the-odin-project","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"top-working-with-text","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":true,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-links-and-images/links-and-images-lesson-a","prevChallengePath":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-working-with-text/working-with-text-lesson-i","id":"637f4e5172c65bc8e73dfe26","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":15,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-working-with-text/working-with-text-lesson-j"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}